title: unsorted
pid: 64d7566a-cd5b-472d-85fc-251e1e395ae2
body: |2-
  This note is about the unsorted relationship I use in my notes.
  If container R contains node U which consists entirely of
  a link to this 'unsorted' node and some content,
  then each content of U is related to R,
  in a way that I hope to someday better specify. 
